{"title":"矩阵的导数运算(1)","uid":"d97c1a68285e6aac869410b1223c6673","slug":"Math/矩阵的导数运算1","date":"2023-02-10T08:37:00.000Z","updated":"2023-04-15T02:31:18.360Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Math/矩阵的导数运算1.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h1 id=\"矩阵的导数运算-1\">矩阵的导数运算 (1)</h1>\n<h2 id=\"标量方程对向量的导数\">标量方程对向量的导数：</h2>\n<p>定义： <span class=\"math display\">\\[\n\\frac{\\partial f(\\vec{y})}{\\partial\n\\vec{y}}=\\begin{bmatrix}\\frac{\\partial f(\\vec{y})}{\\partial\ny_1}\\\\\\frac{\\partial f(\\vec{y})}{\\partial y_2}\\\\\\vdots\\\\\\frac{\\partial\nf(\\vec{y})}{\\partial y_m}\\end{bmatrix}_{m\\times 1}\n\\]</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\"math inline\">\\(f(\\vec{y})\\)</span> - 标量 [<span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(1\\times1\\)</span>]</li>\n<li><span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\vec{y}=\\begin{bmatrix}y_1\\\\y_2\\vdots\\\\y_m\\end{bmatrix}_{m\\times1}\\)</span>\n- 向量 [<span class=\"math inline\">\\(m\\times1\\)</span>]</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>求导结果的行数与分母相同，称为<strong>分母布局</strong>(Denominator\nLayout)</p></blockquote>\n<p><span class=\"math display\">\\[\n\\frac{\\partial\nf{\\vec{y}}}{\\partial\\vec{y}}=\\begin{bmatrix}\\frac{\\partial\nf(\\vec{y})}{\\partial y_1}&amp;\\frac{\\partial f(\\vec{y})}{\\partial\ny_2}&amp;\\dots&amp;\\frac{\\partial f(\\vec{y})}{\\partial\ny_m}\\end{bmatrix}_{1\\times m}\n\\]</span></p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>行数和分子相同，称为<strong>分子布局</strong>(Numerator Layout)</p></blockquote>\n<p><strong>例</strong></p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(f(y_1, y_2) = y_1^2+y_2^2\\)</span>，<span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\vec{y}=\\begin{bmatrix}y_1\\\\y_2\\end{bmatrix}\\)</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"math display\">\\[\\frac{\\partial f(\\vec{y})}{\\partial\n\\vec{y}}=\\begin{bmatrix}\\frac{\\partial f(\\vec{y})}{\\partial\ny_1}\\\\\\frac{\\partial f(\\vec{y})}{\\partial\ny_2}\\end{bmatrix}=\\begin{bmatrix}2y_1\\\\2y_2\\end{bmatrix}\\]</span>\n分母布局</p>\n<p><span class=\"math display\">\\[\\frac{\\partial f(\\vec{y})}{\\partial\n\\vec{y}}=\\begin{bmatrix}\\frac{\\partial f(\\vec{y})}{\\partial\ny_1}&amp;\\frac{\\partial f(\\vec{y})}{\\partial\ny_2}\\end{bmatrix}=\\begin{bmatrix}2y_1&amp;2y_2\\end{bmatrix}\\]</span>\n分子布局</p></blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"向量方程对向量的导数\">向量方程对向量的导数</h2>\n<p><span\nclass=\"math display\">\\[\\vec{f}(\\vec{y})=\\begin{bmatrix}f_1(\\vec{y})\\\\f_2(\\vec{y})\\\\\\vdots\\\\f_n(\\vec{y})\\end{bmatrix}_{n\\times1}\\]</span>\n<span\nclass=\"math display\">\\[\\vec{y}=\\begin{bmatrix}y_1\\\\y_2\\\\\\vdots\\\\y_m\\end{bmatrix}_{m\\times1}\\]</span>\n<span class=\"math display\">\\[\n\\frac{\\partial\\vec{f}(\\vec{y})_{n\\times1}}{\\partial\\vec{y}_{m\\times1}}=\\begin{bmatrix}\\frac{\\partial\nf(\\vec{y})}{\\partial y_1}\\\\\\frac{\\partial f(\\vec{y})}{\\partial\ny_2}\\\\\\vdots\\\\\\frac{\\partial f(\\vec{y})}{\\partial\ny_m}\\end{bmatrix}=\\begin{bmatrix}\\frac{\\partial f_1(\\vec{y})}{\\partial\ny_1}&amp;\\frac{\\partial f_2(\\vec{y})}{\\partial\ny_1}&amp;\\dots&amp;\\frac{\\partial f_n(\\vec{y})}{\\partial y_1} \\\\\n\\vdots&amp;\\ddots&amp;&amp;\\vdots\\\\\n\\frac{\\partial f_1(\\vec{y})}{\\partial y_m}&amp;\\frac{\\partial\nf_2(\\vec{y})}{\\partial y_m}&amp;\\dots&amp;\\frac{\\partial\nf_n(\\vec{y})}{\\partial y_m}\\end{bmatrix}\n\\]</span> 分母布局</p>\n<h3 id=\"常用特例\">常用特例</h3>\n<p>若 <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\vec{y}=\\begin{bmatrix}y_1\\\\\\vdots\\\\y_m\\end{bmatrix}_{m\\times1}\\)</span>,\n<span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(A=\\begin{bmatrix}a_{11}&amp;\\cdots&amp;a_{1m}\\\\\\vdots&amp;\\ddots&amp;\\vdots\\\\a_{m1}&amp;\\cdots&amp;a_{mm}\\end{bmatrix}_{m\\times\nm}\\)</span>, 则 <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac{\\partial\nA\\vec{y}}{\\partial\\vec{y}}=A^T\\)</span></p>\n<hr />\n<p>若 <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\vec{y}=\\begin{bmatrix}y_1\\\\\\vdots\\\\y_m\\end{bmatrix}_{m\\times1}\\)</span>,\n<span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(A=\\begin{bmatrix}a_{11}&amp;\\cdots&amp;a_{1m}\\\\\\vdots&amp;\\ddots&amp;\\vdots\\\\a_{m1}&amp;\\cdots&amp;a_{mm}\\end{bmatrix}_{m\\times\nm}\\)</span> , 则 <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac{\\partial\\vec{y}^TA\\vec{y}}{\\partial\\vec{y}}=A\\vec{y}+A^T\\vec{y}\\)</span>.\n当 A 为对称矩阵时，<span class=\"math inline\">\\(A^T=A\\)</span>, <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac{\\partial\\vec{y}^TA\\vec{y}}{\\partial\\vec{y}}=2A\\vec{y}\\)</span></p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.